ingredients: INGREDIENTS FOR FISH: TILAPIA, WATER, PALM OIL, VEGETABLE OIL (SOYBEAN, CANOLA AND/OR COTTONSEED OIL), CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF THE FOLLOWING: GARLIC POWDER, GRILL FLAVOR (PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL AND COTTONSEED OIL), ONION POWDER, NATURAL FLAVOR, DEHYDRATED LEMON PEEL, SALT, CORN STARCH, SPICES, GELATIN, SUGAR, DEHYDRATED GARLIC, NATURAL SMOKE FLAVOR, DEHYDRATED ONION, CORN SYRUP SOLIDS, LEMON JUICE SOLIDS, EXTRACTIVES OF PAPRIKA (COLOR), SODIUM TRIPOLYPHOSPHATE (TO RETAIN MOISTURE).
